skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: physics formulae
des:
Physics Formulae is designed to give you any formulae relating to physics that you may need. 

Upon asking for a formula, Alexa will give you a detailed description to help you learn or to jog your memory. 

This skill is perfect for secondary school aged students who are just starting to learn the fundamentals of physics.

This skill features a constantly expanding database of known formulae and we are constantly looking to expand further. Feel free to suggest formulae that should be added in later updates!
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
